item.title: I need to learn how to make my own server
item.dc:creator: @Iamadam Iamadam
item.description:
@Iamadam wrote:

Firstly, this should probably be in the prvate server section.
Secondly, mopar isnt a server, its a client.
Thirdly, mopar works GREAT. There is no lag caused by it - the only lag would be due to slow servers.
Fourthly (is that even a word;)?), learn java first. You have no hope of creating a client better than mopars unless you have ALOT of experience. ALOT.
Try www.seangreasley.com
